725178f-a.title: Queens: 29th Street - Ditmars Boulevard
725178f-a.text:
29th Street (left), at the N.E. corner of Ditnars Boule-
vard, showing a Roman Catholic shrine, bedecked with American
flags. Cn the left is the Catholic Imnaculate Conception
School.
P. L. Sperr  Mwy 27, 1934
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
